library(conflicted)
library(tidyverse)
library(mvtnorm)
library(patchwork)

# 
set.seed(0)
individual <- matrix(abs(rnorm(200)), ncol = 2)

# 1
individual1 <- individual[,1] / sum(individual[, 1]) 

# 2
individual2 <- individual[, 1] * 0.6 + individual[, 2] * 0.4
individual2 <- individual2 / sum(individual2)

df <- data.frame(X = individual1, Y = individual2)

p1 <- df |>
  pivot_longer(everything()) |>
  mutate(X2 = rep(c(1:100), 2)) |>
  ggplot(aes(x = X2, y = value, fill = name)) +
  geom_col() +
  scale_fill_manual(values = c( "red","blue")) +
  labs(
    x = "ID",
    y = "",
    title = "2",
    fill = ""
    ) +
  theme(aspect.ratio = 1/2) #

p2 <- df |>
  ggplot(aes(x = X, y = Y)) +
  geom_point(alpha = 0.5) +
  geom_smooth(method = "lm", formula = y ~ x, se = FALSE) +
  labs(x = "X", y = "Y") +
  theme(aspect.ratio = 1) #

library(conflicted)
library(tidyverse)
library(patchwork)

# 
# 2
x <- rmvnorm(
  n = 100,
  mean = c(0, 0),
  sigma = matrix(c(1, 0.8, 0.8, 1), nrow = 2)
  ) 

# 
my_std <- function(x) {
  (x - min(x)) / (max(x) - min(x))
}

# 
x1 <- my_std(x[, 1])
x2 <- my_std(x[, 2])

# 
heatmap1 <- matrix(x1, nrow = 10, ncol = 10)
heatmap2 <- matrix(x2, nrow = 10, ncol = 10)

# 
hm1 <- heatmap1 |>
  as.data.frame() |>
  pivot_longer(everything()) |>
  mutate(name2 = paste0("W", sort(rep(1:10, 10)))) |>
  ggplot(aes(x = name, y = name2, fill = value)) +
  geom_tile() +
  scale_fill_gradientn("value", colours = gray.colors(12, start = 0, end = 1, gamma = 2.2, alpha = 1)) +
  theme(
    aspect.ratio = 1,
    axis.text = element_blank(),
    axis.title = element_blank(), 
    axis.ticks = element_blank(),     
    legend.position = "none"
  ) +
  labs(title = "X")

hm2 <- heatmap2 |>
  as.data.frame() |>
  pivot_longer(everything()) |>
  mutate(name2 = paste0("W", sort(rep(1:10, 10)))) |>
  ggplot(aes(x = name, y = name2, fill = value)) +
  geom_tile() +
  scale_fill_gradientn("value", colours = gray.colors(12, start = 0, end = 1, gamma = 2.2, alpha = 1)) +
  theme(
    aspect.ratio = 1,
    axis.text = element_blank(),
    axis.title = element_blank(), 
    axis.ticks = element_blank(),     
    legend.position = "none"
  ) +
  labs(title = "Y")

p3 <- data.frame(x1, x2) |>
  ggplot(aes(x = x1, y = x2)) +
  geom_point(alpha = 0.5) +
  geom_smooth(method = "lm",formula = y ~ x, se = FALSE, color = "blue") +
  labs(x = "X", y = "Y") +
  coord_fixed() + #  
  scale_x_continuous(limits = c(0,1)) +
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0,1))

1.1.7

library(conflicted)
library(tidyverse)
library(MASS)

n <- 190     # 
low <- -0.45 # 
high <- 0.95 # 
rho <- 0.7   # 
mean <- c(0, 0) # 

Sigma <- matrix(c(1, rho, rho, 1), nrow=2) # 

set.seed(0)
data <- mvrnorm(n = n-1, mu = mean, Sigma = Sigma) # 

x <- data[,1]
y <- data[,2]

x <- low + (high - low) * (x - min(x)) / (max(x) - min(x)) # x
y <- low + (high - low) * (y - min(y)) / (max(y) - min(y)) # y

x <- c(x, 0.80) # 
y <- c(y, 0.72) # 

df <- data.frame(x = x, y = y)

df |>
  ggplot(aes(x = x, y = y)) +
  geom_point(alpha = 0.5) + # 
  geom_smooth(method = "lm", formula = y ~ x, se = FALSE) + # 
  geom_point(aes(x = 0.80, y = 0.72), colour = "red", size = 2) + # 
  coord_fixed() + # 
  annotate("text", x = -0.25, y = 0.75, size = 4,
           label=paste0("r = ", round(cor(df$x, df$y), 2))) +
  labs(
    x = "",
    y = "",
    title = "2"
  )

library(conflicted)
library(tidyverse)
library(igraph)

pref_ja <- c(
  "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "",
    "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "",
    "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "",
    "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "",
    "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "",
    "", ""
    )

pref_ja <- factor(pref_ja, levels = pref_ja)

# 
data_df <- read_csv(
  "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/tkEzaki/data_visualization/main/1%E7%AB%A0/data/matrix.csv"
  )

# 
data_matrix <- data_df[, -1] |>
  as.matrix(nrow = 47)
diag(data_matrix) <- 0
data_matrix <- log1p(data_matrix)
rownames(data_matrix) <- colnames(data_matrix) <- pref_ja

# 
threshold <- quantile(data_matrix, .95)

# 
gData <- data_matrix |>
  as.data.frame() |>
  rownames_to_column(var = "pref") |>
  pivot_longer(!pref) |>
  rename(
    from = pref,
    to = name,
    weight = value
  ) |>
  dplyr::filter(weight >= threshold)

# 
g <- graph_from_data_frame(gData, directed=TRUE)
E(g)$width <- E(g)$weight/5
E(g)$color <- rainbow(100, alpha = 0.5)[round(E(g)$weight/max(E(g)$weight) * 100, 0)]

V(g)$label.cex <- 1
V(g)$size <- 20

g |>
  plot(
    layout = layout_in_circle,
    edge.curved = 0.5,
    edge.arrow.size = 0.5
    )

  ggplot(aes(x=val)) + 
  geom_histogram(aes(y=after_stat(density)), bins=30, color = "black", fill = "gray") +
